         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">21 June 1864 ¶ Dear Sir, ¶  ¶ At your departure from Australia permit me to offer you my little photograph ¶ An album of photographs presented to Neumayer at the time of his departure from Melbourne i...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">64.06.21</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Georg Neumayer</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Sammlung Nebauer, Handschriftenabteilung, Universitätsbibliothek, Leipzig.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">21./6/64</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Verehrter Herr!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Erlauben Sie mir Ihnen bei Ihrem Scheiden von Australien mein Bildchen als ein geringes Andenkens-Zeichen anzubieten, und mir das Ihre für die Sammlung der mir befreundeten grossen Zeitgenossen zu erbitten.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Herrn Professor Neumayer</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">21 June 1864</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>At your departure from Australia permit me to offer you my little photograph<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>An album of photographs presented to Neumayer at the time of his departure from Melbourne is in the Neumayer-Archiv, Museum für Naturkunde, Bad Dürkheim. It includes a copy of the photograph of M published in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>R.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Pescott (1982), p. 34.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>as a small token of remembrance, and to ask for yours for my collection of great contemporaries<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>who are my friends.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>No image of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Neumayer<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>has been identified at MEL, but see M to J. Haast, 29 July 1862 (in this edition as 62-07-29b) and notes thereto.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Professor Neumayer</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c</p>
         </div>
